metadata.name: Birthday Present
metadata.description:
So, my little sisters birthday is coming up, and this is a surprise for her. She made this piece for school and I tried to convince her to get into art and NFT's.

Maybe this can change her mind and might join the space. All profit raised from this will either be given to her on her birthday 29/03 or used to buy her some NFT's recommended by the community and held in her wallet.  
I will let the community decide this as well.

There is also one surprise I have for the new owner.  
TBA.
